12:16.300 --> 12:17.567
-(police radio chatter)

12:17.600 --> 12:19.333
-I'm not gonna listen to you
stand out here and yell

12:19.367 --> 12:21.667
and scream at her anymore.
I'm tired of listening to it.

12:21.700 --> 12:23.700
The reason you're going to jail
is because of a warrant

12:23.733 --> 12:25.233
that you got by
not wearing a seatbelt.

12:25.267 --> 12:27.233
So you yelling at her
about her causing this

12:27.267 --> 12:29.267
