because she didn't cause this.

12:29.300 --> 12:31.467
-Oh, she just finished it.
-It's just the chance
of the fact that

12:31.500 --> 12:33.867
we ended up here,
and you had a warrant.
-Come on. We're done.

12:33.900 --> 12:36.433
-You're fact is over, man.
You're not gonna
convince me of nothing.

12:36.467 --> 12:38.467
I'm not trying to convince you.
