for me for a second.

13:02.800 --> 13:04.600
Hey, sir?

13:04.633 --> 13:06.233
Stop.

13:06.267 --> 13:08.733
-We having fun yet?

13:08.767 --> 13:10.233
-Yep.
-We'll put this
on your head now.

13:10.267 --> 13:12.067
-You're in a helmet, 'cause
