to this lady?

13:16.633 --> 13:18.967
-Because she deserves it.
-She doesn't deserve this.

13:19.067 --> 13:20.500
Well, John--
-You're an idiot.

13:20.533 --> 13:22.333
-I'm sorry you feel the way
that you do about all this.

13:22.367 --> 13:23.767
Hope you have
a better night, okay?

13:26.267 --> 13:28.067
-I was headed to work one night
about three years ago

13:28.067 --> 13:29.600
when my daughter
was three years old,

13:29.633 --> 13:31.433
and she gave me
a little stuffed giraffe

13:31.467 --> 13:34.067
and a hair clip that she told me
she wanted me to keep

13:34.100 --> 13:35.867
so that the bad guys
didn't get me.

13:35.900 --> 13:39.100
I keep my giraffe in my bag
and keep my hair clip
in my pocket,

13:39.133 --> 13:40.733
and I've had it
with me ever since.

13:40.767 --> 13:43.933
And that's part of what
keeps you going some nights

13:43.967 --> 13:46.600
whenever the stresses
start getting to you.

13:46.633 --> 13:48.233
-Right now we're trying to
catch up to a vehicle

13:48.267 --> 13:51.700
that has made
a few traffic violations,

13:51.733 --> 13:53.467
and they're driving
a little crazy, so...

13:53.500 --> 13:55.967
we're gonna see
if we can't find out
what's going on with him.

