giving it to them, dude.

18:09.233 --> 18:10.400
(chuckles)

18:10.433 --> 18:13.600
Just because, man,
I'm just kind of trying...

18:13.633 --> 18:16.600
make up for all the things
that I've just done in my past.
-Sure.

18:16.633 --> 18:18.967
Let me talk to my partner
real quick. Give me one second.
-Okay.

18:21.067 --> 18:22.633
-Not enough to go with.
-Yeah.

18:22.667 --> 18:24.800
-So you think it could be,
like, full on DUI?

18:24.833 --> 18:26.467
Work it, or...
-Yeah.

18:26.500 --> 18:28.933
Well, uh, talking to him,

18:28.967 --> 18:30.767
he's repeated
the same story three times.

18:30.800 --> 18:32.200
-Oh, I figured.
The way he was talking--

18:32.233 --> 18:33.767
-He, uh...

18:33.800 --> 18:36.333
his pupils are, like,
the size of a pin.

18:36.367 --> 18:39.200
