18:50.200 --> 18:51.500
(clears throat)

18:51.533 --> 18:53.067
-I'm under arrest, right?

18:53.067 --> 18:54.267
-No.
-Oh, okay.

18:54.300 --> 18:56.167
-Do you have anybody
you could call for a ride?

18:56.200 --> 18:57.767
-No, sir. Ah, man, I just--

18:57.800 --> 19:00.667
-From what he's saying,
you smell a little bit more
like alcohol

19:00.700 --> 19:02.267
than what you're saying,
and you're being cool.

19:02.300 --> 19:05.333
