a cool dude, man.

19:46.067 --> 19:47.600
I wish I could have met you
on a different note.

19:47.633 --> 19:49.933
-Have a better night, okay?
-You, too.

19:49.967 --> 19:52.467
-132 and Bush,
I've got him at gunpoint.

